{
  "page_id": "5061188880",
  "title": "01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup",
  "version": 2,
  "url": "/spaces/CARSFW/pages/5061188880/01-+CUBAS+RTA-RTE+Setup",
  "last_modified": "2024-11-28T08:06:24.000+01:00",
  "last_modified_by": "WU Jianqiang (XC-CP/ESW2-CN)",
  "parent_id": "5061188613",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step by Step guideline to configure RTA-RTE in AEEE Pro:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1. Create workspace for the project"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2. Load AEEE Pro latest version from toolbase 2023.2.0.2"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "3. Load AEEE cfg  project in AEEE Pro."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-37-56.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-37-56.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Figure 1 : Go to project location and select the configurations"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-38-50.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-38-50.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Figure 2 : Select SAIL_MASTER and click finish."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "4. Enable RTA-RTE Build action."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-42-33.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-42-33.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RTE_EXE should link to rtarte tools which install in toolbase."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-56-57.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-56-57.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Figure 3: Enable RTE build Action"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-1-31_10-19-46.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-1-31_10-19-46.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Figure 4: Click OK"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "5. Open variants.mic file and select RteBuildAction.bamf"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-43-32.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-43-32.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "6. Pop-Up window will appear. Select OK"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-2-5_14-49-36.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-2-5_14-49-36.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "7. In build action window RTARTE_Generation will be enable"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-44-10.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-44-10.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "8. RTA-RTE generation action is added to the project."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "9. Clean and reload the project and build the project."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RTA-RTE action require per-requisit arxml file and modules to be part of bamf action. Below are the required per-requisit,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "a) System Description"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "b) System"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "c) Ecu Instance"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "d) Composition"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "e) Ecu Extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The files are not part of delivery, Build action terminates with error code E002991. For details description of error verify RteErr.xml file."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "10. How to creat and generate the above files not go into detail here, can refer to the well written wiki page:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RTE Startup Configuration - XC-CT China - Docupedia"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "11. relate report error , we can refer to the RTE Document \" RTA-RTE Error Description.pdf\" (note:\\toolbase\\rtarte\\12.2.0_a_spinlock\\Documents)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": ">> BUILD SUCCESS"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": ">> Verify RTE folder"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-58-31.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-58-31.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": ">> Verify OS function call"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "a) Verify Rte_Task_C0_10ms.c function call, Rte_Task_C*_*ms used for scheduled SWC Runables which Communication with RTE."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-59-58.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_14-59-58.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "b) Verify Rte_Task_C0_10ms_Dummy.c function call, this dummy task not used for project build and just for RTE code generate success, the bsw main task functions are manual coding in Task_C0_*ms()"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/01-%20CUBAS%20RTA-RTE%20Setup/image-2024-11-28_15-0-38.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/01- CUBAS RTA-RTE Setup/image-2024-11-28_15-0-38.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "--------------------------------------------------END-----------------------------------------------------------"
    }
  ],
